        "subject": "LU-10850 osd: remove phantom entries from IAM indexes",
        "message": "LU-10850 osd: remove phantom entries from IAM indexes\n\nWhen creating IAM indexes we include an initial zeroed-out entry (key\nand record) This serves no known purpose and may confuse some index\nusers. So stop including this phantom entry.\n\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\nChange-Id: If0c97ccb71688c60e9157746dba6b583212f25f1\n"
